[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=VoxType Grammar Check
Name[zh_CN]=VoxType 最近输入语法检查
Comment=Check the most recently inserted VoxType transcript locally
Comment[zh_CN]=在本地检查 VoxType 最近插入的文本
